# Renderly

**Renderly** is a minimalistic Python web framework built around [Mako templates](https://www.makotemplates.org/). With Renderly, all you need to do is drop `.template` files in a directory â€” and your app is live. Itâ€™s perfect for small apps, prototypes, and template-driven workflows.

